cu.explanation_en: Setting amf_ip_address.ipv4 to an invalid IP address '999.999.999.999' will cause AMF connection failures and NG interface establishment issues.

du.explanation_en: Setting dl_absoluteFrequencyPointA to 0 will cause invalid downlink frequency configuration and transmission failures.
du.explanation_zh: 將 dl_absoluteFrequencyPointA 設定為 0 會導致無效的下行鏈路頻率配置和傳輸失敗。
